						               													<description>Set in a Nordic universe, Neverheim was established as an experimental planet by the gods! All the races from the realms were put together on one planet to see what would happen! They didn&amp;lsquo;t realise what chaos would be created&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this tactical minatures game Champions from many realms go head to head in battle or team-up to take on the enemy. In this game, your footing can be the difference between success &amp;amp; failure! An extensive cooperative campaign for 1-4 players set in an apocalyptic dystopia.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Goddess of Death has raised the Army of the Dead &amp;amp; infiltrated the realms with carnage and corruption. Team-up with gods, giants and champions from across universe and unlock the power to overcome this zombie apocalypse! Throughout the campaign you will be levelling-up constantly to become more and more powerful as you progress while the battles get bigger and bigger!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game has RPG elements and there is multiple towns where you will find blacksmiths, alchemists, mystics, healers, tradesmen etc. Familiars add another level to the combat and can be a ferocious companion. An in-depth experience with multiple game modes and rich lore to discover!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
